  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Feeling like part of the future; at JFK sitting in translucent yellow chairs with an A380 rolling by and reflecting on a great <strong>MakerFaire</strong></p>

      <li class="embed-link js-actionEmbedTweet" data-nav="embed_tweet">
        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>
      </li>
  </ul>
</div>

</div>

  </div>

      </div>

      

      


      
        <div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize  js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Calling all hobbyists! We have the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/BeagleBoard?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>BeagleBoard</b></a>, HawkBoard and EVAL BOT in the <a href="https://twitter.com/hashtag/MakerFaire?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b><strong>MakerFaire</strong></b></a> yellow tent. Stop by and check it out</p>
